<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us — GameVault</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/support.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favi.png">
</head>
<body class="support-page">
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
            <img src="/images/favi.png" alt="" width="30" height="30">
            Game<span>Vault</span>
        </a>

        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/games">Games</a></li>
            <li><a href="/support/support">Contact</a></li>
            <% if (user && user.role === 'admin') { %>
            <li><a href="/admin-dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>

        <div class="nav-actions">
            <div class="auth-buttons">
                <% if (locals.user) { %>
                <span class="user-welcome">Welcome, <%= user.name %></span>
                <form action="/logout" method="get" class="logout-form">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-login">Logout</button>
                </form>
                <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-login">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-register">Register</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hamburger">
            <div class="line1"></div>
            <div class="line2"></div>
            <div class="line3"></div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="support-main">
        <div class="support-header">
            <h1>Contact <span>Us</span></h1>
            <p>Reach our support team — we're here to help with orders, accounts, and more.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-cards">
            <div class="contact-card gv-card">
                <div class="contact-card-icon"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></div>
                <h3>Email Support</h3>
                <p class="contact-value">support@gamevault.com</p>
                <p class="contact-note">Response within 24 hours</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-card gv-card">
                <div class="contact-card-icon"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i></div>
                <h3>Phone Support</h3>
                <p class="contact-value">+1 (555) 123-4567</p>
                <p class="contact-note">Mon–Fri, 9 AM – 5 PM EST</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-card gv-card">
                <div class="contact-card-icon"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i></div>
                <h3>Live Chat</h3>
                <p class="contact-value">Available on our website</p>
                <p class="contact-note">24/7 for Premium members</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="faq-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked <span>Questions</span></h2>
            <div class="faq-list">
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How do I get a refund for a game?</summary>
                    <p>Digital purchases are eligible for a refund within 14 days if the game has been played for less than 2 hours. Submit a request via email with your order number and we'll process it within 3–5 business days.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How quickly will I receive my game key?</summary>
                    <p>Most keys are delivered instantly to your account dashboard and email after payment is confirmed. Pre-orders are delivered on release day.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>I forgot my password — what should I do?</summary>
                    <p>Use the "Forgot Password" link on the login page, or contact support with your registered email and we'll help you regain access within 24 hours.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Which payment methods do you accept?</summary>
                    <p>We accept major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex) as well as PayPal. All transactions are encrypted and secure.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Can I gift a game to someone else?</summary>
                    <p>Yes! During checkout, select "Send as Gift" and enter the recipient's email. They'll receive the key directly with an optional personal message.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>My game key isn't working — help!</summary>
                    <p>Double-check you're redeeming on the correct platform (Steam, Epic, etc.). If the issue persists, contact support with your order ID and a screenshot of the error.</p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>
    <script>
        window.addEventListener('scroll', function () {
            const navbar = document.querySelector('.navbar');
            if (window.scrollY > 50) navbar.classList.add('scrolled');
            else navbar.classList.remove('scrolled');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
